Harvey Goldhersz
Chief Data Officer & CEO, GroupM Analytics

Linkedin





X







Harvey Goldhersz
Chief Data Officer & CEO, GroupM Analytics


Linkedin



                                                                            In August 2014, Harvey Goldhersz was appointed GroupM Chief Data Officer and CEO of Analytics. In this role he is responsible for ensuring GroupM agencies and their clients have superior access to the data-led insights that can truly transform their media initiatives and performance.Goldhersz joins GroupM from MediaCom, where he has served as Vice Chairman and Worldwide COO for a decade. Prior to 2004, Goldhersz was founder and CEO of MediaCom Digital and CEO of Beyond Interactive, ultimately merging four separate entities – Beyond Interactive, MediaCom Digital, media.com, and Grey E-Media. Under his leadership, MediaCom became the largest integrated interactive media agency network in the industry as ranked independently by RECMA.Prior to his current position, Goldhersz had been CEO of MediaCom North America since 2011.He is based at GroupM’s Headquarters in New York City.
                                                                        












